Description: Calculates nitrogen fertilization requirements following the 
    Disciplinari di Produzione Integrata (DPI) Emilia-Romagna – method of the 
    balance (Allegato 2). It implements the nitrogen balance model used by 
    FertDPI / Fert_Office and accounts for crop demand (A), soil supply (B), 
    leaching (C1, C2), immobilization (D), previous crop residues (E), organic 
    fertilization (F_org), and natural deposition (G). Includes soil texture 
    classification (USDA and DPI groupings), maximum allowed doses (MAS), 
    NDVI-based variable rate estimation (calibration and Holland & Schepers), 
    and tools for integrated and precision nitrogen management.
